\c 43
\nb
\v 1 Ngahlulela, Nkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 26.1.\x*, umele udaba lwami esizweni esingesabi uNkulunkulu\x + 1 Sam. 24.15.\x*; ungikhulule emuntwini wenkohliso longalunganga.
\v 2 Ngoba wena unguNkulunkulu wesiphephelo sami\x + Hlab. 31.4.\x*; ungilahleleni\x + Hlab. 44.9.\x*? Ngihambelani ngikwezimnyama ngenxa yocindezelo lwesitha\x + Hlab. 42.9.\x*?
\v 3 Thumela ukukhanya kwakho leqiniso lakho, kungikhokhele, kungise entabeni yakho engcwele\x + Hlab. 2.6.\x* lemathabhanekeleni akho\x + Hlab. 84.1.\x*.
\v 4 Khona ngizakuya elathini likaNkulunkulu, kuNkulunkulu injabulo yentokozo yami; yebo ngizakudumisa ngechacho, Nkulunkulu, Nkulunkulu wami.
\p
\v 5 Udanelani mphefumulo wami? Njalo ukhathazekelani phakathi kwami? Themba kuNkulunkulu, ngoba ngisezamdumisa, ukusiliswa kobuso bami, loNkulunkulu wami\x + Hlab. 42.5,11.\x*.